// Business Law (views/law/business.pug)
extends ../layouts/main

block content
  .law-container
    .container
      h1 Business Law
      .law-section
        h2 Step 1: What is Business Law about?
        p Business law governs the formation, operation, and regulation of businesses and commercial activities. It encompasses various legal aspects of running a business, including registration, licensing, compliance, contracts, and dispute resolution.
        p This area of law covers different business structures (sole proprietorship, partnership, company, LLP), regulatory compliance, business transactions, and protection of commercial interests. It ensures fair business practices and protects stakeholders' rights.
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 2: Why do we need Business Law and Solutions?
        h3 Why We Need Business Law:
        ul
          li Regulation of business activities and practices
          li Protection of business interests and intellectual property
          li Fair competition and market practices
          li Investor and consumer protection
          li Dispute resolution and contract enforcement
        h3 Solutions:
        ul
          li Proper business registration and licensing
          li Compliance with regulatory requirements
          li Contract drafting and review
          li Intellectual property protection
          li Risk management and legal compliance
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 3: Help and Description
        h3 Key Areas of Business Law:
        .business-areas
          .area-card
            h4 Business Registration
            p Procedures for different business structures
          .area-card
            h4 Financial Discipline
            p Accounting, auditing, and financial compliance
          .area-card
            h4 Business Licensing
            p Required licenses and permits for operations
          .area-card
            h4 Business Filing
            p Annual returns and compliance filings
          .area-card
            h4 Contracts
            p Drafting, review, and enforcement of agreements
        h3 Business Structures:
        ul
          li Sole Proprietorship: Simple ownership structure
          li Partnership: Two or more persons sharing business
          li Limited Liability Partnership (LLP): Limited liability with partnership flexibility
          li Private Limited Company: Separate legal entity with limited liability
          li Public Limited Company: Shares available to public
        h3 Important Compliance:
        ul
          li ROC filings for companies
          li GST registration and compliance
          li Income tax obligations
          li Labor law compliance
          li Environmental clearances (if applicable)
      
      .chatbot-section
        h2 Business Law Chatbot
        .chatbot-container
          .chat-messages#chat-messages
            .message.bot-message
              p Welcome! I can help you with business law queries. What would you like to know about registration, licensing, or business compliance?
          .chat-input-container
            input(type='text', id='chat-input', placeholder='Ask about business law...', class='law-chat-input')
            button#send-btn Send